in everyday life.

00:08:00.440 --> 00:08:02.210
But even if it's being used

00:08:02.210 --> 00:08:04.990
as an umbrella term,
it's not a neutral term.

00:08:04.990 --> 00:08:07.490
I mean, it has a very
specific [inaudible] baggage

00:08:07.490 --> 00:08:08.860
