'80s Islamic movements started

00:08:18.820 --> 00:08:22.540
to look not like the
typical Islamism.

00:08:22.540 --> 00:08:24.620
And so they looked for
alternative concepts.

00:08:24.620 --> 00:08:28.880 position:56%
Moderate Islam was one of them plus
Islamism, Muslim hood, neo-Islamism,

00:08:28.880 --> 00:08:32.810
but I think what we find in
Turkey requires a very clear break

00:08:32.810 --> 00:08:35.500
from the concept of Islamism,
so that's the first reason

00:08:35.500 --> 00:08:38.600
that I wanted to term
this with a new label.

00:08:38.600 --> 00:08:40.110
Also I wanted this term

00:08:40.110 --> 00:08:43.410
to communicate the
content of this new form.

00:08:43.410 --> 00:08:47.350
Now, so one key element of
this new form that its hybrid.

00:08:47.350 --> 00:08:48.790
It doesn't reject nor submits,

00:08:48.790 --> 00:08:51.460
but it creates hybrid
institutions and practices.

00:08:51.460 --> 00:08:55.730
And the other key element is
that it's individual orientation.

00:08:55.730 --> 00:08:58.870
So basically the question
Muslims must ask is,

00:08:58.870 --> 00:09:03.580
