while taking part in modernity?"

00:09:03.580 --> 00:09:07.210
And so there neither state
oriented nor society oriented.

00:09:07.210 --> 00:09:10.750
The goal isn't Islamization
of the state from top-down

00:09:10.750 --> 00:09:14.270
or nor it is Islamization
of the community bottom

00:09:14.270 --> 00:09:17.220
up to eventually create
an Islamic state.

00:09:17.220 --> 00:09:19.050
And this is not individualism.

